        <mxCell id="forumposttag" value="&lt;b&gt;ForumPostTag&lt;/b&gt;  «junction»&#xa;──────────────────────────────&#xa;FK  post → ForumPost&#xa;FK  tag → ForumTag&#xa;→ many-to-many junction" style="shape=mxgraph.basic.rect;dx=10;fillColor=#BBDEFB;strokeColor=#1E88E5;fontColor=#1A237E;rounded=1;arcSize=8;whiteSpace=wrap;html=0;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=4;spacingBottom=4;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Consolas;" vertex="1" parent="g6">
